- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper deals with speech data. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel interactive attention mechanism for training an end-to-end ST model. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with developing a model for speech recognition and translation, which are both AI-related tasks. 
- cs.SD (Signal Processing) is another possible category as the paper deals with processing speech signals.
